subject: Re: Junit Installation
msgSnippet: I have extracted all of the sources from the jfree.chart, jfree.report, jfree.common, and then also the junit src.jar file, and have imported these sources
messageBody:
I have extracted all of the sources from the jfree.chart, jfree.report, jfree.common,
and then also the junit src.jar file, and have imported these sources into an Eclipse
workspace. This has established a baseline that ALMOST compiles.

The sources reference other objects/classes that are not defined. For instance,
the "HttpSessionBindingListener" is not known. The binary data for the class is
found within the classes jar file,... but the source for this class does not seem to be
provided within the downloadable materials.

Where might I find the source for this class?
